    %h2 Sarah Butler

    %p
      Sarah is an author and literary consultant. Her debut novel Ten Things I’ve Learnt About Love is published by Picador in the UK, Penguin Press in the US, and in 14 other countries around the world.  She has been a writer in residence for Great Ormond Street and on the Central Line, and she runs UrbanWords which manages literature-based projects that engage with the process of regeneration. www.urbanwords.org.uk

