    %h2 Molly Naylor

    %p
      Molly is a poet and scriptwriter whose first solo show, Whenever I Get Blown Up I Think Of You debuted at the Edinburgh Festival Fringe in 2010 before touring internationally. Her second live show My Robot Heart was a collaboration with band The Middle Ones and was supported by Battersea Arts Centre, Bristol Old Vic, The Junction Cambridge and Escalator. She devised and delivered interactive storytelling project Made Up in collaboration with Byron Vincent. www.mollynaylor.com
